version_description: You can play along with the song from CD. There is no capo used and if you can sing like Steve Lukather this version is perfect.
There were no tabs of this amazing song at ultimate guitar, so I wanted to change that.
Easiest way to play this song by using a capo, chord legend included.
The original song was composed and recorded on a Roland synth guitar from 1980. These chords are a close approximation of what was played to my ears.
